Attribution and prior work
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The five signal families in this benchmark mirror and generalize the author's
prior work as well as external benchmarks. Please cite the corresponding work
when using or discussing a specific family:

  - time         mirrors GroundClock / NowBench (github.com/mthamil107/groundclock)
  - access-deny  mirrors "Will the Agent Recuse Itself?" (arXiv:2606.06460)
  - memory-label mirrors memorywire (arXiv:2606.01138)
  - injection    mirrors "Beyond Pattern Matching" (arXiv:2604.18248) and the
                 external InjecAgent benchmark (arXiv:2403.02691,
                 github.com/uiuc-kang-lab/InjecAgent)
  - bot-policy   mirrors ai-bot-shield

"In-Band Signal Compliance" and "IBSC" are used here as descriptive framework
names. No trademark rights are asserted.
